<h2>Rating: 55/100</h2>

<p>(<em><b>Formula for the Rating System</b>: number of tracks I feel emotionally connected to / total number of tracks</em>)</p>

<h2>Album Description:</h2>
<p><b>Artist</b>: Frank Turner<br />
<b>Year</b>: 2008 <br />
<b>Type</b>: Compilation Album</br />
<b>Personal Notes</b>: The First Three Years is basically all the songs that didn't make it on the albums and LPs from Frank Turner's first three years as a solo artist. I usually end up liking compilation albums, covers, and rare songs more than singles and the studio albums.</p>

